              Space prop
            </.link>
          </.heading2>

          <.cp>
            The space prop offers values such as <.custom_inline_code>extra_small</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>small</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>medium</.custom_inline_code>, <.custom_inline_code>large</.custom_inline_code>, and <.custom_inline_code>extra_large</.custom_inline_code>. These values control the vertical spacing between elements within the form labelas and descriptions and input.
          </.cp>

